Grimlock lands beside Repugnas, a huge thud shakes the ground. He moves
in, instinctivly, and sniffs Repugnas with his head sideways. "If you
Autobot, how come you fight in our base?" He asked, growling softly,
wondering were Slag and Sludge were.
